FBIS4-40188 "drsov115_b_94010" FBIS-SOV-94-115 Daily Report 14 Jun 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Military, Nuclear & Space Issues Export Controls Imposed on Biological War Materials Export Controls Imposed on Biological War Materials LD1406165494 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1630 GMT 14 Jun 94 LD1406165494 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent] [Text] Moscow June 14 TASS -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin signed today a resolution imposing a strict control on exports of gene materials which could be used in a biological warfare. The list of substances under control includes "pathogenes ... and their genetically changed forms, fragments of genetical material and equipment, which could be used in preparation of bacteriological (biological) and toxic weapons", the presidential press service reported. [ellipses as received]
